final_desc: - Dengan poli(vinil klorida) :Kain tekstil diresapi, dilapisi, ditutupi atau dilaminasi dengan plastik, selain yang dimaksud dalam pos 59.02.;- With poly(vinyl chloride) :Textile fabrics impregnated, coated, covered or laminated with plastics, other than those of heading 59.02.

- Lain-lain :Kain tekstil diresapi, dilapisi, ditutupi atau dilaminasi dengan plastik, selain yang dimaksud dalam pos 59.02.;- Other :Textile fabrics impregnated, coated, covered or laminated with plastics, other than those of heading 59.02.
